The roasted plantain which is one of Nigerians favourite roadside snack is locally known as Boli and can also be prepared at home. As all you need to prepare it is just plantain which could either be ripe or unripe according to your preference and a microwave oven. If you have ever been frustrated at not being able to meet your boli cravings then watch this quick and easy steps to prepare Boli at home. 